{"tid":52362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南港島綫】金鐘站終於有廁所 男廁焗促用家話「出晒汗」","createTime":"2016-12-24T04:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T12:37:33.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b56da62fb552cbb477dcab4f455ee382e9ab96c2","tid":52362,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161224/large/1482552537_8ee3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161224%2Flarge%2F1482552537_8ee3.jpg&h=12348286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今日早上10時至下午2時舉行南港島綫車站開放日，需付費入閘參觀的金鐘站在開放前，亦有40多人等候參觀新擴建部分。因應南港島綫通車，金鐘站內新設兩個洗手間，一個在L5未來沙中綫月台層，即南港島綫月台上一層，另一個則在車站大堂的新收費區範圍。<br />\n<br />\n年逾70歲的陳伯今早與家人特意到場參觀金鐘站擴建部分。他說，整體滿意車站設計，惟站內指示仍略嫌不足，若非今天有大量工作人員指示，恐怕自己會迷路。他又指，L5層的男廁廁格位置通風略為焗促，「用到出晒汗」，離開廁格才感到涼意。"},{"pid":"b5e1d3bc3abd5f4c3d1df41fcbfacecc71f9e032","tid":52362,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用到出汗"},{"pid":"ec0d07691bf370b26ce6ff76ccd8d961ef794e12","tid":52362,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2709407b540bbb4c00a14adf31682f0fecf9d16a","tid":52362,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"成班男人一齊痾到出晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d0b8b70f635f8451e39202db8145485350e1c8","tid":52362,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"「用到出晒汗」，離開廁格感到腳軟"},{"pid":"2815d5398c39a536a042cb800bef58bd14e3b1d2","tid":52362,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\